title: Grateful Dead Live at Capital Centre on 1990-03-15
lineage: Dat > Sony PCM r500 > Tascam DA-3000 > Flac 16/48
description: Set 1 Jack Straw Sugaree Easy To Love You Walkin' Blues Althea Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues Tennessee Jed Cassidy Don't Ease Me In Set 2 China Cat Sunflower > I Know You Rider Samson & Delilah Terrapin Station > Jam > Drums > Jam > I Will Take You Home > Wharf Rat > Throwing Stones > Not Fade Away Encore: Revolution This date is featured on Terrapin Limited. reviews.review_text:
Good Recording Hot show!  I was 15 rows back on the floor during Terrapin standing in the aisle when the a-hole security started checking for tickets.  The cap center was notorious for being extremely strict. 

Either way, get this show!  Best Terrapin I saw (I think).
